patch_version = &"v0.1.2"
patch_notes = "New Features:
-Patch Notes Screen has been added.
-Color Scheme across all assets has been redone to soften design language while still being readable.
-Multirail 3 has been added, tested and verified.

Bug Fixes:
-Fixed layout issues with the following buildings
     -Smelter
     -Rail Support
     -Rail Modulator 3

 Miscellaneous:
-Further clean-up of program assets to remove more unused assets. This should lend to better performance.
 "
